\E\xi=\int_{0}^{\th}\frac{1}{\th}x\d x=\frac{1}{\th}\left.\frac{x^{2}}{2}\right\vert _{0}^{\th}=\frac{\th}{2}\implies\th=2\E\xi,\ \th^{*}=2\bar{\mathbf{x}}.
