\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\mathbf{B}^{2}=\begin{pmatrix}1/n & \dots & 1/n\\
\vdots & \ddots & \vdots\\
1/n & \dots & 1/n
\end{pmatrix}^{2}=\begin{pmatrix}n\cdot1/n & \dots & n\cdot1/n\\
\vdots & \ddots & \vdots\\
n\cdot1/n & \dots & n\cdot1/n
\end{pmatrix}=\mathbf{B}.
\]

\end_inset

 Значит, 
\begin_inset Formula $\bar{\mathbf{x}}^{2}\indep s^{2}.$
\end_inset


