\end_inset

 и, по ЦПТ, 
\begin_inset Note Comment
status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout
\begin_inset Formula $\hat{\rho}\sim N$
\end_inset

?
\end_layout

\end_inset


\begin_inset Note Comment
status open

