\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\hat{\bb}_{W}=(\X^{\T}\W\X)^{-1}\X^{\T}\W\y
\]

\end_inset

 есть 
\begin_inset Quotes fld
\end_inset

взвешенная
\begin_inset Quotes frd
\end_inset

 оценка.
 При 
\begin_inset Formula $\W=\Ib$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $\hat{\bb}_{W}=\hat{\bb}$
\end_inset

